last night.

1104
00:54:13,000 --> 00:54:15,330
And you know this how?

1105
00:54:15,360 --> 00:54:17,800
I know.

1106
00:54:19,500 --> 00:54:23,330
We're still in the land
of cartoon people, right?

1107
00:54:23,360 --> 00:54:26,300
I'd really like to see
where they lived,

1108
00:54:26,330 --> 00:54:27,860
this boy and his mother.

1109
00:54:27,900 --> 00:54:30,030
We've already had
a detective out there,

1110
00:54:30,060 --> 00:54:32,060
but, sure, you're welcome
to take a look.

1111
00:54:35,060 --> 00:54:36,130
Hey, hold on a second.

1112
00:54:36,160 --> 00:54:38,260
