1115
00:54:46,760 --> 00:54:48,460
It just doesn't work that way.

1116
00:54:48,500 --> 00:54:50,700
A lot of times,

1117
00:54:50,730 --> 00:54:53,160
the people closest to me...

1118
00:54:53,200 --> 00:54:56,760
I didn't even know you were ill.

1119
00:54:56,800 --> 00:54:58,960
I do know
