1162
00:57:49,050 --> 00:57:50,650
Mine.

1163
00:57:52,680 --> 00:57:54,310
I know what you're thinking.

1164
00:57:54,350 --> 00:57:57,010
You're thinking,
what am I gonna do, kill you?

1165
00:57:59,710 --> 00:58:01,680
I don't know what I'm gonna do.

1166
00:58:01,710 --> 00:58:03,310
But I will figure something out.

1167
00:58:03,350 --> 00:58:07,210
I am gonna make your death

1168
00:58:07,250 --> 00:58:10,210
