1169
00:58:18,710 --> 00:58:20,510
She's mine.

1170
00:58:25,710 --> 00:58:28,710
Hey, Ariel?

1171
00:58:28,750 --> 00:58:30,750
Ariel, sweetie,
come here for a second.

1172
00:58:35,210 --> 00:58:36,910
Hey, come here.
What are you doing?

1173
00:58:36,950 --> 00:58:38,310
I thought you
were changing.

1174
00:58:38,350 --> 00:58:40,810
I thought we were
going to the mall.
We are, we are.

1175
00:58:40,850 --> 00:58:42,250
Just have a look
around the room.

1176
00:58:42,280 --> 00:58:43,350
Okay.

1177
00:58:43,380 --> 00:58:45,410
What am I
looking for?

1178
00:58:45,450 --> 00:58:46,850
I don't know.
What do you see?

1179
00:58:46,880 --> 00:58:49,550
Do you see anything?

1180
00:58:49,580 --> 00:58:51,010
What are you
talking about?

1181
00:58:51,050 --> 00:58:52,550
I see what you see.

1182
00:58:52,580 --> 00:58:53,610
It's your room.

1183
00:58:53,650 --> 00:58:56,110
It looks like your
room always looks.

1184
00:58:56,150 --> 00:58:57,310
Are you okay?

1185
00:58:57,350 --> 00:58:58,580
Yeah, I'm fine.
I'm just curious.

1186
00:58:58,610 --> 00:59:00,280
So...

1187
00:59:00,310 --> 00:59:03,650
