1300
01:03:56,580 --> 01:03:57,880
What is it, Mommy?

1301
01:03:57,910 --> 01:03:59,310
Who's on the phone?

1302
01:03:59,350 --> 01:04:00,680
Hold on.

1303
01:04:00,710 --> 01:04:01,680
