1602
01:18:01,950 --> 01:18:04,710
vouching for the painting's
authenticity?

1603
01:18:04,750 --> 01:18:06,980
Well, I'd have no choice.

1604
01:18:16,250 --> 01:18:17,710
Sorry about that.

1605
01:18:17,750 --> 01:18:19,680
Mm.
I appreciate this.

1606
01:18:20,930 --> 01:18:24,130
And let me present you
with this.

1607
01:18:24,160 --> 01:18:25,700
And this is?
That...

1608
01:18:25,730 --> 01:18:28,200
