1615
01:18:42,600 --> 01:18:45,160
So, on the back,
where it would do no damage,

1616
01:18:45,200 --> 01:18:46,860
I wrote the initials, "C.B."

1617
01:18:46,900 --> 01:18:48,830
in indelible marker.

1618
01:18:48,860 --> 01:18:51,560
That is the painting
that you gave back to me.

1619
01:18:54,760 --> 01:18:57,130
And, yes, it's the real
actual painting.

1620
01:18:57,160 --> 01:18:59,930
But it's not the painting
I brought to your house.

1621
01:19:07,160 --> 01:19:09,160
No initials.

1622
01:19:09,200 --> 01:19:11,100
The painting

1623
01:19:11,130 --> 01:19:14,260
I brought to your house was the
one you had Olga Bankova paint.

1624
01:19:16,800 --> 01:19:17,830
What are you suggesting?

1625
01:19:17,830 --> 01:19:20,360
What are...
What are you talking about?

1626
01:19:20,400 --> 01:19:21,400
Those home invaders

1627
01:19:21,430 --> 01:19:23,560
worked for you,
Mr. Gardner.

1628
01:19:23,600 --> 01:19:24,760
So did Olga.

1629
01:19:24,800 --> 01:19:26,560
Although we're fairly
certain she had

1630
01:19:26,600 --> 01:19:28,960
no idea what she vas involved
in until it was too late.

1631
01:19:29,000 --> 01:19:31,100
When you realized I was going
to pay you a visit,

1632
01:19:31,130 --> 01:19:32,730
you thought I might be
on to something.

1633
01:19:32,760 --> 01:19:34,630
So you gave me
the authentic painting

1634
01:19:34,660 --> 01:19:36,030
to throw me off the scent.

1635
01:19:36,060 --> 01:19:37,860
This is preposterous.

1636
01:19:37,900 --> 01:19:39,300
DEVALOS:
Really?

1637
01:19:39,330 --> 01:19:42,600
What about the part where you
suggested to your hired killers

1638
01:19:42,630 --> 01:19:45,130
that you needed them
to hit one more home-- yours.

1639
01:19:45,160 --> 01:19:46,630
But, unlike everyone else,

1640
01:19:46,660 --> 01:19:48,660
you weren't surprised when they
showed up-- you were waiting.

1641
01:19:52,360 --> 01:19:53,360
You can't prove that.

1642
01:19:53,400 --> 01:19:55,100
Oh, I think we can.

1643
01:19:55,130 --> 01:19:56,360
What was your story--

1644
01:19:56,400 --> 01:19:57,900
waiting at the top
of the stairs?

1645
01:19:57,930 --> 01:20:00,060
We think maybe you were
hiding at the bottom.

1646
01:20:00,100 --> 01:20:02,230
DEVALOS:
According to ballistics,

1647
01:20:02,260 --> 01:20:03,900
