1652
01:20:12,300 --> 01:20:14,360
Detective, read this
man his rights.

1653
01:20:14,400 --> 01:20:17,460
You have the right
to remain silent.

1654
01:20:17,500 --> 01:20:19,260
Anything you say
can and will be

