1660
01:20:32,130 --> 01:20:34,430
It wasn't just me;
I had a lot of help.

1661
01:20:34,460 --> 01:20:35,460
Yeah, I know,
your daughter.

1662
01:20:35,500 --> 01:20:36,460
The cartoons.

1663
01:20:36,500 --> 01:20:38,430
Yeah, and an old friend.

1664
01:20:38,460 --> 01:20:41,060
Well, thank him for me, too.

1665
01:20:41,100 --> 01:20:44,330
Yeah, well, if I see him,
